text: Maiti is an Indian surname that may refer to *Abha Maiti (born 1925), Indian politician *Ajit Kumar Maiti (born 1928), Indian neurophysiologist *Kalobaran Maiti (born 1967), Indian physicist *Mrigendra Nath Maiti, Indian politician *Samarpan Maiti (born 1988), Indian scientist, human rights activist and model *Souvik Maiti (born 1971), Indian chemist ==See also== *Maiti Nepal, a non- profit organization helping the victims of sex trafficking
title: Maiti
